        "text": "最早来的工人来领的时候，以为必定可以多得一点工钱，谁知也各得一个银币。"
      },
      "cnv": {
        "version_id": "CNV",
        "version_name": "新譯本",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "最先作工的人也來了，以為會多得一點，但每個人也是領到一個銀幣。"
      },
      "cunp": {
        "version_id": "CUNP",
        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "及至那先雇的來了，他們以為必要多得；誰知也是各得一錢。"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "When those hired first came, they thought that they would receive more; but each of them also received a denarius."
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "So when those came who were hired first, they expected to receive more. But each one of them also received a denarius."
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "When those hired first came to get their pay, they assumed they would receive more. But they, too, were paid a day’s wage."
      }
    },
